snippet.title: Ace Attorney Investigations Collection - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Not so fast! Ace Attorney Investigations Collection is out now on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Windows, and Steam! Meet prodigious prosecutor Miles Edgeworth and the colorful cast of family, friends, and foes that put our protagonist’s patience and sharp mind to the test. Take up the chase once more in pursuit of the truth!

Official Website:
https://www.ace-attorney.com/investigations1-2/

#AceAttorneyInvestigations #Capcom
